summary: Play as Evelyn, a beautiful hybrid human/elf.
descriptionHtml:
[b]***IMPORTANT***[/b]
[b]Make sure you install this MANUALLY... here's how[/b]

[color=#ffff00]Copy the file inside the zip folder and paste into your Presets folder which is located in...

Program Files(x86) > Steam > steamapps > common > Skyrim > Data > SKSE > Plugins > CharGen > Presets

...If you don't have those folders then create them.  Once that part is done, load your racemenu ingame by typing in console showracemenu

Then click the presets tab while in racemenu and load this preset for High Elf.
[/color]
[b][color=#ff0000]P.S
The mods needed to get the exact look of Evelyn are shown below and in the last screenshot!
[/color][/b]SG Female Eyebrows - http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35327/?
The Eyes Of Beauty - http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?
KS Hairdos - http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/70363/?
Better Females - http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2812/?

[color=#00ff00]Please enjoy! ;)[/color]
